Package com.packager

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FilterLogger  
    IFilter
    this is an interface created for the various Filters we have
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppFilter
    this is the main class of our app
    BlurFilter
    this class could be used to apply a blur filter on an image opened as a matrix, using opencv's methods
    BnWFilter
    this class could be used to apply a grayscale (black n'white) filter on an image opened as a matrix, using opencv's methods
    DilateFilter
    this class could be used to apply a Dilatation on an image opened as a matrix, using opencv's methods
    FilterLoggerFile
    this class is used to write message in a log file, to register all operation we had made, with the date and time
    FilterZeTeam
    this class could be used to apply a magnificent filter on an image opened as a matrix, by printing a message on it (supposed to be our team's name) thanks to opencv's methods. not usable for now
    OpenIni
    this class is used to open an ini file
  • Exception Summary
